  <brief_title>Ibuprofen Lozenge in Acute Sore Throat Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Efficacy and Safety of V0498 Versus Placebo in Acute Sore Throat Pain.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pierre Fabre Medicament</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pierre Fabre Medicament</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of repeated doses of a low
      dosage of oromucosal Ibuprofen form (lozenge) versus placebo in patients suffering from acute
      sore throat pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
